Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.71,0:00:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀河天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.05,0:00:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼？為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.15,0:00:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危機，這下糟糕了\N緊張！緊張！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撲克光線BURU  BURU
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.72,0:00:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙大騷動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.02,0:00:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK，胡鬧一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.99,0:00:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也沒關係，吃個飲茶\N好啊！好啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.56,0:00:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著歡悅的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.90,0:00:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後一起向神明祈禱吧\NBANG  BANG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.14,0:00:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因果報應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.57,0:00:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天都是冒險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.34,0:00:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.21,0:00:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就讓它順其自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.85,0:00:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有機關，沒有魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.58,0:00:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤注一擲的I.N.G.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.55,0:01:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無憂無慮的狂歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.12,0:01:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夢想與希望的機關鎗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.89,0:01:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鎖定想要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.30,0:01:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,BANG  BANG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.30,0:01:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跳舞吧，玩吧，BRAVO！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.94,0:01:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐上令人興奮的火箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.67,0:01:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開闢天下無敵的成功之路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.55,0:01:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(產地直銷，綜合天使拼盤)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.43,0:01:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀呼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.53,0:01:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭花幹勁十足呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.53,0:01:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就由她去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.07,0:01:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,金凱德建築公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.17,0:01:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可說是銀河屬一屬二的\N宇宙大承包商呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.14,0:01:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且社長這麼年輕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.51,0:01:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好帥喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.65,0:02:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是為什麼建築公司的社長\N會被人盯上呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.38,0:02:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該有什麼隱情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.09,0:02:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是神明所賜予的試鍊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.26,0:02:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管他什麼都好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.76,0:02:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之\N我們做好社長的保鑣就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.80,0:02:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是說不定我會被社長看上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.90,0:02:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞不好有機會釣上金龜婿呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.24,0:02:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？\N我臉上沾了什麼東西嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.31,0:02:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,金...金凱德建築公司的社長\N就是你嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.95,0:02:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就是社長吉姆金凱德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.82,0:02:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可...可是，這個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.02,0:02:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔，這是我年輕時的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.56,0:02:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,霍普，你弄錯了對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.76,0:02:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，社長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.30,0:02:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不小心...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.43,0:02:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.90,0:02:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,金龜婿如何了啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.80,0:02:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別開玩笑了\N我可是閉月羞花的大閨女耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.94,0:03:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問，聽說社長被人盯上了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.01,0:03:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，我收到了恐嚇信\N上面寫著說要殺我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.85,0:03:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了，被下毒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.25,0:03:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！霍普\N怎麼把砂糖加成鹽巴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.26,0:03:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,社長對不起，我又不小心...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.13,0:03:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的有人盯上他嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.53,0:03:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托朗斯巴皇軍的天使隊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.17,0:03:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如何？很美的星球吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.68,0:03:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.34,0:03:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好想住在這麼漂亮的地方喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.88,0:03:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以天使隊的低薪\N是不可能住得起啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.05,0:03:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.05,0:03:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這星球是改建成渡假專用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.25,0:03:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再過一個月的時間\N就要完工了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.33,0:03:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次我是來視察的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.46,0:03:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有什麼仇人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.20,0:03:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.87,0:04:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算殺了我\N也沒有什麼好處啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.14,0:04:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就你個人來說\N有沒有跟人有過節呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.01,0:04:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不起來耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.04,0:04:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係啦\N我們會好好保護社長安全的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.38,0:04:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，奇怪，奇怪...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.22,0:04:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,霍普，怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.55,0:04:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,操縱桿失靈了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.95,0:04:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.19,0:04:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,霍普，把它停下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.73,0:04:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停不下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.56,0:04:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不是保鑣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.83,0:04:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快想想辦法呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.73,0:04:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也無法可想啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.91,0:04:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，修好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.71,0:04:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有被人入侵過電腦的跡象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.68,0:04:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來恐嚇信這件事情\N並不是騙人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.19,0:04:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,金凱德先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.32,0:04:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的沒有什麼線索嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯...沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.76,0:05:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次又怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.90,0:05:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像停止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.30,0:05:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用妳說，我也知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.67,0:05:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個時候，敲一下就會好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.34,0:05:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，弄壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.94,0:05:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，看妳做了什麼好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.24,0:05:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把門打開不就好了，把門打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.48,0:05:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開了\N佛特好厲害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.29,0:05:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接著搞不好會換成步道故障
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.26,0:05:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停的話，走過去不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.49,0:05:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？薄荷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.96,0:05:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從剛才開始\N總覺得好像被人窺視的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.27,0:05:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.27,0:05:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.67,0:05:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個吊燈在搖晃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.81,0:05:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感覺好危險的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.77,0:05:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說它會掉下來嗎？\N不可能啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.28,0:05:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，真的掉下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.15,0:05:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險！會觸電的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.92,0:06:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思\N不客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.09,0:06:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，又掉下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.80,0:06:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.64,0:06:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,社長\N還是回公司比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.27,0:06:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.24,0:06:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.98,0:06:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是照預定行程視察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.68,0:06:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,霍普，接下來去哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.41,0:06:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.18,0:06:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,30分鐘後去大氣工廠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.15,0:06:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,社長，如果又發生危險的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.02,0:06:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,僱用你們來\N就是為了這種時候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.32,0:06:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.29,0:06:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茶泡好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.46,0:06:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳來這裡到底是做什麼的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.13,0:06:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有"蒙德星"的橘子紅茶\N還有親手烤的小餅乾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.14,0:06:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我吃吃看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.90,0:06:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯！好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.51,0:06:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.87,0:06:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.38,0:06:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.84,0:06:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,情況好像不太妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.05,0:07:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位機器人，工作辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.75,0:07:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快逃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.10,0:07:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優，妳在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.03,0:07:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒙德星的茶具...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.00,0:07:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別管了，快過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.64,0:07:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那好貴的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.16,0:07:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼會朝這邊來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.69,0:07:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們的目標不是社長嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.49,0:07:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭花，我腳好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.23,0:07:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要叫了，快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.30,0:07:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目標A，進入23區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目標B，往18區移動當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.67,0:07:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.15,0:08:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐那個可以逃走嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.02,0:08:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.96,0:08:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳知道怎麼操作嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.72,0:08:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨便按按就會動啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.00,0:08:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.34,0:08:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再這樣下去，我們會變成槍靶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.54,0:08:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有什麼武器呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.37,0:08:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個看起來可以當武器用喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.68,0:08:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.32,0:08:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去沒完沒了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.69,0:08:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，有個按鈕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.19,0:08:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,按下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大氣改造工廠...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.63,0:09:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞蘭少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.67,0:09:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.37,0:09:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭，又追上來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.04,0:09:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.21,0:09:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犯人好像\N對我們的行蹤瞭若指掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.45,0:09:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽不懂妳在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.05,0:09:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理社長行程表的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.38,0:09:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該就是你吧，霍普先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.95,0:09:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，這個...那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.49,0:09:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，這和霍普無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.62,0:09:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真正的犯人在那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.63,0:09:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這...這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.40,0:09:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是我的孫子亞蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.47,0:09:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是照片上的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.10,0:09:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實我被人盯上這件事是假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.94,0:09:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.88,0:09:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實我是要測試你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.78,0:09:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,測試？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.95,0:09:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.71,0:09:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了尋找我孫媳婦的測試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.72,0:09:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孫媳婦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.25,0:09:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我們工作上的危險很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.85,0:09:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以想找\N像你們這樣強悍的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.42,0:09:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來當我孫子的伴侶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.56,0:10:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那要從我們之中選一個媳婦囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.26,0:10:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.00,0:10:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了我們之外\N你還找過其他人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.20,0:10:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，通過第一次審查的\N大約有500人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.34,0:10:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞蘭，決定如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.04,0:10:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天第一次審查的結果是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.24,0:10:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.71,0:10:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,體力、精力、判斷力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.15,0:10:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根據種種要素審核的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.88,0:10:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很遺憾，只有一個人不合格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.09,0:10:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有一人不合格？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.15,0:10:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，合格的有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.16,0:10:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.69,0:10:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從剛才就一直\N聽你們胡說瞎說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.80,0:10:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們應該也有選擇的權利吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.37,0:10:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我知道\N我已經通過第一次審查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.17,0:10:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但不好意思，我要拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.01,0:10:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我雖然也應該合格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.91,0:10:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但還是免啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.11,0:10:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.75,0:10:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.29,0:11:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...氣死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.86,0:11:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.69,0:11:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是怕自己沒通過\N才說要拒絕的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.23,0:11:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀，佛特妳才是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.40,0:11:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼可能會落選嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.17,0:11:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.71,0:11:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，到底是誰落選呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.98,0:11:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點想知道耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.38,0:11:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有老天知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.71,0:11:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管他結果是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.48,0:11:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們來比賽\N看誰先回基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.15,0:11:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輸的人要請大家吃晚飯\N開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.85,0:11:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，蘭花妳賴皮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.89,0:11:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優抓緊喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.36,0:11:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！什麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.53,0:11:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該不是我落選吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.70,0:11:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(下個菜單是\N廢校的回憶肉醬，海盜風味)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.70,0:11:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放油時要先把鍋子\N從火上拿開才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.64,0:11:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.61,0:11:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振作點！梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.54,0:11:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.98,0:11:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.98,0:11:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳不能死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.83,0:12:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滿天的星辰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.57,0:12:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像是打翻水瓶似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.81,0:12:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我新月的曲線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.68,0:12:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做了夢之後，變得想見你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.38,0:12:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,側耳傾聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.55,0:12:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，不是聽見了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.43,0:12:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令人興奮的天線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.27,0:12:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要讓它睡著  NO  NO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.47,0:13:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,處女座的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.48,0:13:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向巨蟹座的你發出\N急電，急電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.45,0:13:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乘著飛馬的翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.59,0:13:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前去迎接你
